data.description: Beautiful End of Group Unit 3 level townhome, with three bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a fully finished basement. This house was built in 2019, and has all the bells and whistles! Property includes: a two-car garage and a driveway. Deck is built off of the main level giving a nice peaceful vibe.  Kitchen has stainless steel appliances. Separate dining room area next to the kitchen with a clear view outdoor seating. Breakfast bar/island located in kitchen. Hardwood floors are located on the main level; basement, upper level, and stairs are carpeted. Owner’s suite has a full bath located inside.  Here is the best part...NO more lugging clothes to the basement.  The washer and dryer are conveniently located upstairs on the same level as the bedrooms. There is also a rough-in located in the basement ready for a bathroom install. The neighborhood has an exercise area, playground, and gazebo. Property is located in close proximity to: BWI Airport, Fort Meade Army base and other area attractions , Live Casino. This homes screams Must Have!
